OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FPlans for the 81st Liberation Day in
OL,7,FJersey and Guernsey have been
OL,8,Frevealed, including a weekend full of
OL,9,Fmusic and entertainment.
OL,11,FSaturday 9 May 2026 will mark more
OL,12,Fthan eight decades since the islands
OL,13,Fwere liberated from German Occupation
OL,14,Fafter the Second World War.
OL,16,FIt brings thousands of islanders every
OL,17,Fyear to come together and celebrate
OL,18,Fthe day across both Bailiwicks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
