OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FThe Bailiff of Jersey, Robert MacRae,
OL,7,Fwill be delivering a speech for his
OL,8,Ffirst Liberation Day in the role.
OL,10,F"Having attended Liberation Day
OL,11,Fcommemorations for many years, I have
OL,12,Falways been struck by the powerful
OL,13,Fsense of community and shared
OL,14,Freflection that the occasion brings
OL,15,Facross Jersey," the Bailiff explained.
OL,17,FGuernsey also recently announced the
OL,18,Fline-up of events at Albert Pier.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
