OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FDeputy Andy Cameron, Guernsey's Vice-
OL,7,FPresident and Liberation Day Lead for
OL,8,Fthe Committee for Education, Sport and
OL,9,FCulture, said: "Albert Pier will be a
OL,10,Freal focal point this Liberation Day,
OL,11,Fwith live music spanning everything
OL,12,Ffrom 1940s classics to some of our
OL,13,Fbest contemporary local bands."
OL,15,FJersey's order of events
OL,17,FThe Band of the Island of Jersey will
OL,18,Fassemble in the Royal Square at
OL,19,F9:30am, before the group begins
OL,20,Fmarching at 10:30am.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
