OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FAt 11am, a special sitting of the
OL,7,FStates Assembly will commence in
OL,8,FLiberation Square and feature an
OL,9,Faddress from the Bailiff as Presiding
OL,10,FOfficer, followed by an address given
OL,11,Fby Connetable Philip Le Sueur.
OL,13,FAt 11:20am, Bailiff of Jersey, Robert
OL,14,FMacRae, will give his official welcome
OL,15,Fand address to islanders, followed by
OL,16,Fa Service of thanksgiving given by The
OL,17,FDean of Jersey, The Very Reverend Mike
OL,18,FKeirle.
