OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FFollowing the service, there will be
OL,7,Fthe official re-enactment of Force
OL,8,F135's arrival into Liberation Square,
OL,9,Fand a performance of Beautiful Jersey
OL,10,Fsupported by the Musical Originals.
OL,12,FAt midday, Force 135 will march
OL,13,Falongside the motorcade, with music
OL,14,Fentertainment at Weighbridge Place
OL,15,Fgetting underway at 12:45pm until 8pm.
OL,17,FThe Weighbridge will host a line-up of
OL,18,F1940s-inspired music and dance, along
OL,19,Fwith food vendors and craft stalls.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
