OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FFestivities will continue on Sunday 10
OL,7,FMay, from 10am, with acoustic music,
OL,8,Fmarket stalls, and family-friendly
OL,9,Fentertainment at Weighbridge Place
OL,10,Funtil 5pm.
OL,12,FGuernsey and its musical lineup
OL,14,FGuernsey is hosting its festivities in
OL,15,FSt Peter Port, including its
OL,16,Ftraditional cavalcade and Thanksgiving
OL,17,FService at 10am.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
