OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FThe Albert Pier will become a hub for
OL,7,Fmusic, theatre, and food starting from
OL,8,F11am, with the Town Church Service
OL,9,Fstarting at the same time.
OL,11,FA children's zone and tea tent will be
OL,12,Favailable in Crown Pier.
OL,14,FIslanders can also watch a one-act
OL,15,Fplay, The Child's Fear by Facade
OL,16,FShows, based on a true story from the
OL,17,FOccupation, alongside a wide range of
OL,18,Fmusic acts.
OL,20,FThe celebrations will end at 10:45pm.
