OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FLast year's 80th milestone saw
OL,7,Fthousands gather across the Channel
OL,8,FIslands to mark the end of German
OL,9,FOccupation.
OL,11,FThe Princess Royal visited Guernsey
OL,12,Fand Sark, where Her Royal Highness
OL,13,Fspoke to islanders and attended the
OL,14,Fisland's events.
OL,16,FBroadcaster and barrister Rob Rinder
OL,17,Fco-hosted Guernsey's 80th celebrations
OL,18,Falongside TV personality Rylan at Beau
OL,19,FSejour.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
