OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776272750
OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,FJersey also saw Sir Winston
OL,7,FChurchill's grandson, Sir Nicholas
OL,8,FSoames, join the 80th celebrations.
OL,10,FSir Nicholas attended the island's
OL,11,FService of Thanksgiving and said: "I
OL,12,Freally was deeply impressed by it and
OL,13,FI feel the community's spirit here.
OL,14,FThere's nowhere you can go where
OL,15,Fpeople are so loyal, singing the
OL,16,FNational Anthem with cheers all around
OL,17,Fthe Square.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
