PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776272750
OL,3,CChannel Islands' 81st Liberation Day
OL,4,Ccelebrations revealed
OL,6,F"To see a crew from the Britannia
OL,7,FRoyal Naval College, Dartmouth and the
OL,8,Fequivalent German Naval Cadets
OL,9,Fmarching together is unbelievable.
OL,11,F"Nobody is going to forget what
OL,12,Fhappened. It was very bad, and there
OL,13,Fwere some terrible goings on, but at
OL,14,Fthe end of the day, it's all over,
OL,15,Fthank God."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
